description:
RealSimpleEDU.com brings you on-the-go learning and reference for Human Body Anatomy.

App offers quizzes and tutorials  to help you learn about Human Body Anatomy.

App is continuously updated based on your feedback.Your 100% satisfaction is guaranteed.

App Tools include search .



Includes following tutorials:

Anatomy Basics,
Body Functions and Planes,
Epithelial Tissue I,
Epithelial Tissue II,
Connective Tissue,
Muscle Tissue,
Nervous Tissue I,
Nervous Tissue II,
Cardiovascular System,
Cardiovascular Illustration,
Digestive System I,
Digestive System II,
Endocrine System,
Human Reproduction System,
Male Reproduction Organs,
Female Reproduction Organs,
Integumentary System,
Lymphatic System I,
Lymphatic System II,
Muscular System,
Nervous System,
Respiratory System,
Respiratory Illustration,
Skeletal System,
Urinary System,
Human Bones,
Body Cavities,
Upper Limb I,
Upper Limb II,
Lower Limb.


Includes following quizzes:

Quiz on  Types of Tissues 1,
Quiz on Types of Tissues 2,
Quiz on Nervous Tissue,
Quiz on Integumentary, Lymphatic and Immune System,
Quiz on Muscles,
Quiz on Body Systems,
Quiz on Human Bones,
Quiz on Body Parts.


What is unique about RealSimpleEDU apps? 

1) A touch friendly, quick reference app, which is always in your pocket and always works (no data connection required)

2) A companion app for on-the-go, bite-sized learning 

3) Offers value for money (A lifetime of free updates) 

4) 250,000 paying customers from 155 Countries.


Our Vision: Provide on-the-go references that enable our customers to refer, learn and remember; easy to learn, more engaging and most complete.

Our Mission: A RealSimpleEDU app in every pocket.

Please write to us. We would love to improve this app.
